graph LR
    ODHModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>v1.27.0-rhods-153]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHModelController -->|watches CRDs| KServe[KServe v0.11.0<br/>InferenceService, ServingRuntime CRDs]
    ODHModelController -->|mTLS, routing, telemetry| Istio[Istio v1.17.4<br/>Service Mesh]
    ODHModelController -->|OpenShift Service Mesh| Maistra[Maistra v2.x<br/>ServiceMeshMember, SMCP]
    ODHModelController -->|ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor CRDs| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1]
    ODHModelController -->|creates external routes| OpenShiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes v3.9.0+]
    ODHModelController -->|core platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.26.4]
    ODHModelController -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.14.6<br/>Kubebuilder]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|routes point to| IstioGateway[Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>istio-system namespace]
    ODHModelController -->|RBAC/ServiceMonitors| OpenShiftMonitoring[OpenShift Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus]
    ODHModelController -.->|NetworkPolicy labels| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>opendatahub.io/dashboard=true]

    %% Integration Points
    ODHDashboard -->|UI management| ODHModelController
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto-deploy models| KServe

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    Predictor[Predictor Pods<br/>created by KServe] -->|model artifacts| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS S3, MinIO, etc.]
    Predictor -->|traffic routing| IstioGateway

